      "text": " Verification that a transaction has occurred between two parties resulting in agreement of [[Terms And Conditions]] which result in the authorization of a third party to complete an enabling, supporting transaction.",
      "id": "fd8b6f1c5ddf4a2c69d09b6eb7d14d1d"
